# --- Build output ---
/target
**/target/

# --- Compiled binaries: never publish ---
# The Rust binary embeds local build paths; the plugin binary links proprietary
# Vectorworks object code (redistribution breaches the SDK license). Everyone
# builds their own from source.
/bin/
**/*.vwlibrary
**/*.vwlibrary/

# --- Vectorworks SDK: never publish confidential headers or SDK-derived output ---
**/SDKLib/
**/VectorworksSDK/
**/*VWMM*
**/*.vwr/

# --- Internal / non-public working notes ---
SESSION-HANDOFF.md
*-HANDOFF.md

# --- macOS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
**/xcuserdata/
.playwright-mcp/
